[code]import java.io.IOException;
import java.io.InputStream;
import java.net.URL;
import java.util.ArrayList;
import java.util.List;
import java.util.Random;

public class Main {
public static final List huhhhhhhh = new ArrayList();

public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
	String huh = "qu";
	while(true) {
		huh = huh(huh);
		if(!huhhhhhhh.contains(huh)) {
			huhhhhhhh.add(huh);
			System.out.println(huh + " added, " + huhhhhhhh.size() + " words total");
		} else
			huh = huhhhhhhh.get(new Random().nextInt(huhhhhhhh.size()));
	}
}

private static String huh(String qu) throws IOException {
	InputStream in = new URL("http://suggestqueries.google.com/complete/search?output=firefox&client=firefox&qu=" + qu).openStream();
	byte[] bytes = new byte[0];
	int length = 0;
	byte[] buffer = new byte[4096];
	while((length = in.read(buffer)) != -1) {
		byte[] newBytes = new byte[bytes.length + length];
		System.arraycopy(bytes, 0, newBytes, 0, bytes.length);
		System.arraycopy(buffer, 0, newBytes, bytes.length, length);
		bytes = newBytes;
	}
	String rawWords = new String(bytes).substring(5 + qu.length());
	String[] words = rawWords.substring(0, rawWords.length() - 2).split(",");
	for(int i = 0; i < words.length; i++) {
		String word = words[i];
		if(word.length() <= 0) {
			words[i] = huhhhhhhh.get(new Random().nextInt(huhhhhhhh.size()));
			continue;
		}
		word = words[i].substring(1);
		words[i] = word.substring(0, word.length() - 1);
	}
	String[] huhs = words[new Random().nextInt(words.length)].split(" ");
	return huhs[new Random().nextInt(huhs.length)];
}

}[/code]
